{"body": "Use case:\r\n\r\nI want to preserve the contents `development.log` and clear the `test.log` and `stage.log`. Right now, the `rake log:clear` task will completely empty all of the log files. I wanted a way to limit which logs were cleared when running this task.\r\n\r\nYes, there isn't much difference in the result, I just like using `rake` when I can.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/12345174", "created_at": "2013-01-16T22:54:19Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/8964#issuecomment-12345174", "updated_at": "2013-01-16T22:54:19Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 8964, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mattdbridges/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mattdbridges/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mattdbridges/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/mattdbridges", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mattdbridges/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/mattdbridges", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mattdbridges/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/fa4b5f21ddfec459b530bfce99079e54?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F0f3da53df1c3935c37f47ffbc13d554b.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mattdbridges/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mattdbridges/received_events", "gravatar_id": "fa4b5f21ddfec459b530bfce99079e54", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mattdbridges/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "mattdbridges", "type": "User", "id": 442443, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mattdbridges/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523d609ebd354364b90064f9"}, "id": 12345174, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/8964"}
